desc.html: This is a cropped version of a photo taken by the Newark Photo Studio on September 18, 1925 of a boxing event hosted by Paddy McGuigan to benefit the Harrison NJ P.B.A. McGuigan can be seen standing in the middle of the boxing ring wearing a stripped tie. The complete and original photograph is held at The Henry Mutz Museum of Harrison in Harrison, NJ as of 07/12/2012.
